msgid "So yadeva tattha honti tiṇāni vā paṇṇāni vā tāni ekajjhaṃ saṅgharitvā nisīdāmi pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. "
msgstr "I gather up some grass or leaves into a pile, and sit down cross-legged, with my body straight, and establish mindfulness right there. "

#. VAR: jānāmi → pajānāmi (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.63:10.5"
msgid "So evaṃ jānāmi: "
msgstr "I know this: "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.6"
msgid "‘rāgo me pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṃkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo; "
msgstr "‘I’ve given up greed, hate, and delusion, cut them off at the root, made them like a palm stump, obliterated them, so they’re unable to arise in the future.’ "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.7"
msgid "doso me pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṃkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.8"
msgid "moho me pahīno ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṃkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo’. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.9"
msgid "So ce ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evaṃbhūto caṅkamāmi, ariyo me eso tasmiṃ samaye caṅkamo hoti. "
msgstr "When I’m practicing like this, if I walk meditation, at that time I walk like the noble ones. "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.10"
msgid "So ce ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evaṃbhūto tiṭṭhāmi … pe … "
msgstr "… I stand like the noble ones … "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.11"
msgid "nisīdāmi … pe … "
msgstr "I sit like the noble ones … "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.12"
msgid "seyyaṃ kappemi, ariyaṃ me etaṃ tasmiṃ samaye uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When I’m practicing like this, if I lie down, at that time I lie down like the noble ones. "

msgctxt "an3.63:10.13"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, ariyaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ, yassāhaṃ etarahi nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the high and luxurious bed of the noble ones that I get these days when I want, without trouble or difficulty.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an3.63:11.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bho gotama, abbhutaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, Master Gotama, it’s amazing! "

msgctxt "an3.63:11.2"
msgid "Ko cañño evarūpassa ariyassa uccāsayanamahāsayanassa nikāmalābhī bhavissati akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, aññatra bhotā gotamena. "
msgstr "Who but Master Gotama could get such a high and luxurious bed of the noble ones when he wants, without trouble or difficulty? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.185, sc12
msgctxt "an3.63:12.1"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! "

msgctxt "an3.63:12.2"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya: ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ kho bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. "
msgstr "As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many ways. "

msgctxt "an3.63:12.3"
msgid "Ete mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāma dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. "
msgstr "We go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "an3.63:12.4"
msgid "Upāsake no bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupete saraṇaṃ gate”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember us as lay followers who have gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.63:12.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

